    <summary>Windows Performance Toolkit contains Windows Performance Recorder and Windows Performance Anaylzer - the most recent generation of performance trace capturing and analyzing tools from Microsoft.</summary>
    <description>Allows analysis of Windows Performance via ETW controllers, providers and consumers specifically oriented around analyzing and finding performance problems.
    ATTENTION: This package requires and will automatically install .NET 4.0 if it is not present.
    This installation includes:
    Windows Performance Analyzer (wpa.exe)
    Windows Performance Recorder (wpr.exe)
    xbootmgr (xbootmgr.exe)
    xperf (xperf.exe)
    </description>
  </metadata>
  <files>
    <file src="tools\**" target="tools" />
  </files>
